plmxml_bus:SavedQueryDef.name: WF_Has_Attached_PDF_Dataset
plmxml_bus:SavedQueryDef.Description: Checks if the workflow target has attached Datasets of type PDF and last PDF modifying user is dcproxy

plmxml_bus:QueryClause.stringValue: SELECT qid FROM ItemRevision WHERE "Dataset:IMAN_Rendering.object_type" = "${object_type = PDF}" AND "Dataset:IMAN_Rendering.last_mod_user.user_id" = "${last_mod_user = dcproxy}"
